Proof.
      intro c.
      induction c as [| a' c' IH].

      (* Base case *)
      (* ========================================================= *)
      intros a l H_val.
      destruct l.

      (* 1 case is trivial *)
      (* ========================================================= *)
      discriminate H_val.

      (* 2 case simpl *)
      (* ========================================================= *)
      simpl in H_val. discriminate H_val.

      (* 3 case *)
      (* ========================================================= *)
      simpl in |- *. intros a1 l1 H_val.
      destruct a' as [a' b'].
      destruct (list_eq_dec Bool.bool_dec l1 b') as [| ?].

      (* List is equal *)
      (* ========================================================= *)
      inversion H_val. subst a1. subst b'.
      left. reflexivity. rename a1 into a.
      apply IH in H_val.
      right. assumption.
Qed.
